un-incarcerated brother,
with instructions...

319
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:40,361
- to notify the authorities immediately
- Wow.

320
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:41,851
If I do not answer the phone.

321
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:44,685
- In the room.
